(6, 'Boeung Ket FC rope in first ASEAN COTA player into squad', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Boeung Ket FC signed 24-year-old left-back Scott Woods from the Philippines on Thursday, making him the first ASEAN COTA player in the club.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Woods joined the four-time CPL winners Boeung Ket FC after fulfilling his duty with the Philippines National Football Team in the ASEAN Mitsubishi Electric Cup 2024. Woods played a key role in guiding his side to the tournament&rsquo;s semifinals. However, Thailand defeated them bringing their tournament journey to an end.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Before joining Boeung Ket FC, Woods played for Muangthong United in Thailand&rsquo;s first professional football league.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The CPL altered their regulations for foreign player registration ahead of the season 2023-2024, with each club in the league allowed to register six foreign players, one of whom must be from Asia and another from inside ASEAN.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The CPL hoped to improve league quality and support ASEAN players in doing so, which has hitherto never been done.</p>', 'Admin', '2025-01-07 06:55:31', 'uploads/677ccfe30809a.jpg', 1, 1, '2025-02-06 15:52:59', 318),
(7, 'Cambodia marks ASEAN Sports Day 2024 in Phnom Penh', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cambodia marked on Saturday the ASEAN Sports Day 2024 at the National Olympic Stadium in Phnom Penh to strengthen and promote sports in all ASEAN countries.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The annual event is also aimed to raise people&rsquo;s awareness of the ASEAN and promote a healthy and harmonious lifestyle under the motto of &ldquo;One Vision, One Identity and One Community,&rdquo; said Vath Chamroeun, Secretary of State at the Ministry of Education, Youth and Sports.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Moreover, he continued, the celebration is to inspire the Cambodian people, as well as those of the entire ASEAN community to participate in all kinds of sports to enhance their health, strengthen friendship, solidarity, and communication, and boost the ASEAN sports sector.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">According to Vath Chamroeun, on the same day, Indonesia also celebrated the event and invited Cambodian martial artists to participate and perform Bokator, a traditional sport unique to Cambodia.</p>', 'Admin', '2025-01-07 06:56:40', 'uploads/677cd0284c041.jpg', 1, 1, '2025-02-06 15:53:58', 55),
(8, 'FIFA ranks Cambodia 8th in ASEAN football standings', '<p>The Cambodian National Men&rsquo;s football team is ranked in eighth place out of eleven ASEAN football teams, with Thailand on top based on FIFA football rankings, which were updated on February 15.</p>\r\n<p>In eighth place Cambodian men&rsquo;s football team has made little progress and remains ranked among the bottom half of ASEAN football teams.</p>\r\n<p>The <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cambodia_national_football_team\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Cambodian men&rsquo;s football team</a>, also known as &ldquo;<em><strong>Kouprey</strong></em>&rdquo; &ndash; also nicknamed the &ldquo;forest ox&rdquo; and &ldquo;gray ox&rdquo; &ndash; currently has 931. 47 points in FIFA&rsquo;s ranking system, placing it in 8th position in ASEAN, and 179th overall in world rankings.</p>\r\n<p>The lack of improvement stems from poor performances by both senior and junior football teams in big events last year.</p>\r\n<p>The 32nd Southeast Asian Games in May in Cambodia were the first major disappointment.</p>\r\n<p>Despite great hopes of earning a medal, the Cambodia U22 national football team failed to reach the tournament&rsquo;s semi-final stage. Cambodia won only one of its three group-stage qualification matches.</p>', 'Admin', '2025-01-07 06:57:17', 'uploads/677cd04d30c37.jpg', 1, 1, '2025-02-06 07:43:25', 29),
(10, 'Sixteen kids selected to join Bati National Football School', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Following three days of try-outs, sixteen talented young footballers under fifteen from across Cambodia were selected to attend the Bati National Football and Academy Centre in Takeo province.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bati National Football School, supported by the Football Federation of Cambodia (FFC), held a recruitment session from January 16 to 18 to find new young players for training.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ouk Rina head of administration at the Bati National Football School told Khmer Times yesterday that 50 young athletes from across the kingdom took part in the try-outs.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The FFC announced the final results on Tuesday, awarding scholarships to sixteen youngsters from eleven provinces and cities. He added that students from Mondulkiri and Pailin represented the majority of all the potential footballers who were selected.</p>', 'Admin', '2025-01-07 06:59:27', 'uploads/677cd0cfe4acb.jpg', 1, 1, '2025-02-06 15:53:46', 51),
(11, 'Womenâ€™s football team ready to kick off', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Cambodia National Women&rsquo;s Football Team has spent the last several months training in China in preparation for their second appearance at the upcoming 32nd SEA Games.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The football team, along with other sports teams, was sent to train in China last September, and they will return to Cambodia in late April to compete at the games.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Keo Sarath, secretary-general of the Football Federation of Cambodia (FFC), said the Cambodian women players have been training with Chinese professional football coaches.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">He added that they have had regular friendly matches with professional and other football teams.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;This can be the best help to push them to grow technically and build more confidence on the pitch,&rdquo; he said.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;China has provided mutual technical assistance to help many Cambodian athletes, not just the football team, to prepare for the SEA Games. They (China) have provided training venues, arranged friendly matches, and covered all the basic needs. And that is why we sent them there,&rdquo; said Sarath.</p>', 'Admin', '2025-01-07 07:00:09', 'uploads/677cd0f9bcb8b.jpg', 1, 1, NULL, 9),
(12, 'GTA 6, Nintendo\'s new console and what else to watch out for in 2025 gaming', '<p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\">Even if you were lucky enough to get a new console or games this Christmas, you\'ve probably got your eye on some upcoming releases.</p>\r\n<p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\">And 2025 is shaping up to be a big one.</p>\r\n<p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\">Most agree that 2024 was a painful year for the games industry, with tens of thousands of layoffs and worldwide studio closures.</p>\r\n<p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\">There\'s a hope that things will bounce back - at least in part - next year.</p>\r\n<p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\">And two huge releases in particular are likely to cut through in a big way.</p>\r\n<p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\">Developer Rockstar hasn\'t revealed a huge amount about the new game beyond its dual protagonists and scenes from its fictional, Florida-inspired setting Leonida.</p>\r\n<p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\">The big question on most fans\' minds is whether the release date will slip, as has happened for previous big releases from Rockstar.</p>', 'Admin', '2025-01-07 07:03:04', 'uploads/677cd1a82b0e1.jpg', 1, 4, NULL, 7),
(14, 'Diallo seals 2-2 draw for ManU against Liverpool', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">LIVERPOOL &ndash; Amad Diallo came back to haunt Liverpool with a late equalizer that secured a 2-2 draw for Manchester United against Premier League leader Liverpool on Sunday.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The forward turned home Alejandro Garnacho&rsquo;s cross in the 80th minute at Anfield after Mohamed Salah&rsquo;s penalty had looking like giving Liverpool the win.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Diallo struck at the end of extra time as United beat Liverpool 4-3 in a dramatic FA Cup clash last season and hit a 90th-minute winner against Manchester City last month.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">His goal on Sunday was only worth a point on this occasion, but it halted United&rsquo;s four-game losing run and prevented fierce rival Liverpool from opening up an eight-point lead at the top of the standings.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">United head coach Ruben Amorim, however, was still unhappy.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;It&rsquo;s a point, a deserved point, but it&rsquo;s just one point, and we should get mad. Today we should be really disappointed,&rdquo; he said.</p>', 'Admin', '2025-01-07 07:44:36', 'uploads/677cdb640e7c8.jpg', 1, 1, '2025-02-06 15:53:28', 32),
(27, 'More Possible GTA 6 Actors Discovered', '<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333;\">Online news has identified four more possible&nbsp;<em><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">Grand Theft Auto 6</span></strong></em>&nbsp;actors. All of them have either outright confirmed or at least hinted at being involved in&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/db/video-game/grand-theft-auto-6/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">GTA 6</span></em></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333;\">.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333;\">In April 2024, Rockstar reported that&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/gta-6-jason-lead-voice-actor-leak-grand-theft-auto/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Gregory Connors is the possible voice of one of the&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">GTA 6</span></em>&nbsp;protagonists</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333;\">, whom the previous leaks identified as Jason. The American actor\'s CV, which has since been pulled from the internet, stated that he\'s playing a \"lead\" role in a 2025 Rockstar title, suggesting he\'s either been cast as Jason or perhaps one of&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">GTA 6</span></em>\'s villains.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333; background: white;\">A subsequent investigation by Game Rant has now yielded four more&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/gta-6-jason-lucia-lead-actors-leak-rumor-manni-perez-dylan-rourke/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; background: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">possible&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">GTA 6</span></em>&nbsp;actors</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333; background: white;\">. Two of them have flat-out confirmed their involvement in Rockstar\'s much-anticipated game in their online resumes. This duo comprises Los Angeles-born actor Brandon James Somerville and American actress Stevie Dust, sometimes credited as Stevie Dutson. Somerville revealed that he plays a supporting role in&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">GTA 6</span></em>, while Dust credited herself with unspecified NPC work.</span></p>', 'Admin', '2025-02-06 12:08:44', 'uploads/67a4a64c76436.jpg', 1, 4, '2025-02-06 15:51:20', 9),
(28, 'Apex Legends Making Anti-Cheat and Matchmaking Updates', '<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">In the first&nbsp;<strong><em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">Apex Legends</span></em></strong>&nbsp;developer blog of 2025, Respawn Entertainment has detailed its new armory of weapons to combat hackers and cheaters. Season 24 will bring a host of matchmaking changes aimed at making&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/db/video-game/apex-legends/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Apex Legends</span></em></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;a fairer battleground for all players.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Respawn Entertainment has already promised that 2025 will breathe new life into&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">Apex Legends</span></em>.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/what-to-expect-apex-legends-season-24-takeover-buffs-ttk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm;\">Season 24: Takeover launches on February 11</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">, switching up the battle royale&rsquo;s long-established formula with the aim of making fights faster and more lethal. Assault characters will welcome new buffs, support characters will have their Healing Expert perk nerfed, while the implementation of Arsenals will help freshly dropped legends to dive into the fray.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"adsninja-injected-repeatable-ad-afterend\" style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Anti-cheat Updates Action taken against teaming has resulted in sanctions against 1200 accounts and the removal of 17.4 million ranked points. A brand-new \"future-proof\" machine learning model will soon be deployed to combat bots. A new Report Feedback tool is being developed to provide insights on action taken against reported cheaters. Matchmaking Updates Upcoming measures will help to ensure fair matches including: Unranked Skill Display; seeding skill values; lessening Ranked resets; queue time adjustments; and Ranked Placement matches. Teams of enemy \"Apex Bots\" may be added to low-ranking matches. Bots will not form teams with players. Testing of called-for features such as preferential matchmaking (solos vs. premades) taking place. Focus on future transparency with Apex Legends community. Acknowledging that Apex Legends has suffered a &ldquo;recent increase in bots,&rdquo; Respawn has created &ldquo;a brand-new machine learning model&rdquo; to detect both current bots and &ldquo;future variants and evolutions.&rdquo; This &ldquo;future-proof&rdquo; tool is apparently &ldquo;incredibly accurate with low false negatives&rdquo; and should already be active in-game. Respawn has also targeted teaming in Ranked game modes, where multiple opposing teams join forces to fix the match in their favor. For several months, Respawn has been &ldquo;rolling out new automated teaming detection algorithms, swifter and more severe punishments, and stripping any ill-gotten ranked points from offenders.&rdquo; Around 1200 accounts have faced bans or sanctions, and 17.4 million ranked points have been stripped from their accounts. These Anti-Cheat measures will be a welcome sight to gamers after last year\'s series of issues culminating in the public hacking of the ALGS North American regional final. The developers also stress the importance of reporting cheaters and reveal that they are looking into a system to inform players when action has been taken against a reported account, allowing gamers to see that their actions are making a difference.</span></p>', 'Admin', '2025-02-06 12:09:48', 'uploads/67a4a68c11581.jpg', 1, 4, '2025-02-06 15:51:41', 8),
(29, 'Nintendo Hotel Partnership Rents Out Alarmo Clocks to Guests', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 36.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">Nintendo has partnered with Universal Studios to lend Alarmo clocks to park hotel guests. The partnership gives interested Nintendo fans an opportunity to try out the Alarmo without buying it first.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>Nintendo Alarmo is one of the many surprises that Nintendo has come out with over the years. While the company is best-known for its game consoles and iconic video game franchises like Mario and Zelda, it also has a tendency to be inventive and creative, coming up with unusual releases like Nintendo Labo or Alarmo, or even unusual gaming peripherals, like the Wii Fit Board.</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Hotels Offering Nintendo Alarmo for Rent</span></strong></h2>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Oriental Hotel Universal City</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The Singulari Hotel &amp; Skyspa at Universal Studios Japan</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The Park Front Hotel at Universal Studios Japan Hotel</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Kintetsu Universal City Hotel</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Keihan Universal Tower Hotel</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Universal Port Hotel</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Universal Port Vita</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Like with many Nintendo products, the Alarmo has seen some extreme demand. While it has remained available for sale in the west on the online store, it\'s only been available for Nintendo Switch Online subscribers, possibly in part to prevent excessive scalping. Starting in March 2025, <a href=\"https://gamerant.com/nintendo-alarmo-wider-release-stores-when/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm;\">Alarmo will be available in select retail stores</span></a>, so more fans will get an opportunity to try it then. Meanwhile, in Japan, the Alarmo was set to go on sale in physical stores starting in February, but has since been pushed back to an announced date.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">While some may see the Alarmo as a simple gimmick, it\'s been quite popular with some fans, and tying it into the Univeral Studios Japan park makes some sense. The park is home to Super Nintendo World, and Nintendo encourages fans to use the Alarmo to wake up to a Nintendo-filled day before they head down to the park. There\'s no announcement regarding bringing Alarmo to the western park counterparts, however. If such a collaboration happens, it might be <span style=\"line-height: 107%;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/super-nintendo-world-universal-orlando-layout/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%; color: windowtext; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm;\">when Univeral Studios Orlando opens Super Nintendo World</span></a></span><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\">&nbsp;later in 2025.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Admin', '2025-02-06 12:10:55', 'uploads/67a4a6cf01769.jpg', 1, 4, '2025-02-06 12:12:48', 6),
(30, 'Dead by Daylight Launches New Resident Evil Crossover', '<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Behaviour Interactive has announced&nbsp;<em><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Dead by Dayligh</span></strong></em>t&rsquo;s new crossover with&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Resident Evil</span></em>, scheduled from February 10 to February 25. This collaboration with the highly popular survival-horror franchise will introduce special gameplay, iconic&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Resident Evil</span></em>&nbsp;characters, and a new map to&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/db/video-game/dead-by-daylight/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Dead by Daylight</span></em></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Dead by Daylight&nbsp;</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">offers a thrilling multiplayer experience where players face off in 4v1 matches on a map, with one player assuming the role of the killer while the other four try to find a way to escape.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/dead-by-daylight-killers-best-perks-dbd/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Dead by Daylight</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">&rsquo;s killers come from different horror genres</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">, including slashers and paranormal entities, each with unique abilities to haunt the survivors. The game&rsquo;s setting and vibe have made it perfect for crossovers with other horror franchises like&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Alien</span></em>,&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Child\'s Play</span></em>,&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Ghost Face</span></em>, and&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Resident Evil</span></em>. Now, the developer has announced yet another crossover with Capcom&rsquo;s survival-horror franchise.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">Running from February 10 to February 25,&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/dead-by-daylight-resident-evil-crossover-june-2021/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; background: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Dead by Daylight&nbsp;</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; background: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">brings another&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Resident Evil&nbsp;</span></em>crossover</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">&nbsp;to the game. This time, the thematic additions will be featured in the 2v8 mode, where players can take on the role of&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Resident Evil</span></em>&nbsp;killers like Nemesis and the Mastermind, along with other characters and legendary outfits for players to choose from. Moreover, the 2v8 arena where players will face off is the iconic Raccoon City Police Department, one of the primary settings of&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Resident Evil 2</span></em>, which will also be added to the map rotation. Players will be pleased to know that every character in the crossover will be free to play for the duration of the event.</span></p>', 'Admin', '2025-02-06 12:14:50', 'uploads/67a4a7bad1769.jpg', 1, 4, NULL, 13),
(31, 'Marvel Rivals Players Want Fantastic Four Movie Skins', '<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><em><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: #333333;\">Marvel Rivals&nbsp;</span></strong></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: #333333;\">players are already asking for skins based on&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">The Fantastic Four: First Steps</span></em>, which is set to hit theaters this summer. 2025 is shaping up to be an exciting year for fans of Marvel&rsquo;s First Family, as the Fantastic Four is making a huge return to screens large and small over the next few months. For starters, Mr. Fantastic and the Invisible Woman were added to&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/db/video-game/marvel-rivals/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: #333333; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Marvel Rivals</span></em></a></span><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: #333333;\">&nbsp;</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: #333333;\">as playable characters on January 10, and their teammates The Thing and the Human Torch aren&rsquo;t far behind.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: #333333;\">Meanwhile, Marvel movie fans are gearing up to see the iconic quartet make their MCU debut in&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">The Fantastic Four: First Steps</span></em>, which will arrive in theaters on July 25, 2025. A trailer for the new movie was released earlier this week, giving viewers a look at the&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/fantastic-four-first-steps-trailer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: #333333; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Fantastic Four&rsquo;s retro-style uniforms</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: #333333;\">, The Thing&rsquo;s more comic-accurate CGI design, and even a glimpse of the dreaded Galactus. Overall,&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">The Fantastic Four: First Steps&nbsp;</span></em>is getting plenty of buzz for its futuristic 60&rsquo;s aesthetic, and some gamers are pointing out a prime promotional opportunity for the film ahead of its highly-anticipated release.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333; background: white;\">Shortly after the&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Fantastic Four: First Steps&nbsp;</span></em>trailer was released, Reddit user mighty_and_meaty suggested that NetEase Games release new&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Marvel Rivals&nbsp;</span></em>Fantastic Four skins on July 25 to pair with the movie. They note that since&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/marvel-rivals-thing-human-torch-release-date-guess-prediction/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; background: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">The Thing and the Human Torch</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333; background: white;\">&nbsp;will likely be added to&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Marvel Rivals&nbsp;</span></em>by the time the movie comes out, the timing would be perfect, which is a sentiment many other users on r/marvelrivals agree with.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333; background: white;\">Such a thing wouldn&rsquo;t be unprecedented for&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Marvel Rivals&nbsp;</span></em>either, as&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/marvel-rivals-insomniac-spider-man-skin-more-game-crossovers-good/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; background: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">an alternate Spider-Man skin</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333; background: white;\">&nbsp;based on his Advanced Suit 2.0 from&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Marvel&rsquo;s Spider-Man 2&nbsp;</span></em>was added when that particular game was ported to PC late last month. NetEase has also started offering exclusive rewards to promote&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Captain America: Brave New World</span></em>, including a mystery costume that could be a skin for either Captain America or the Hulk.</span></p>', 'Admin', '2025-02-06 12:15:25', 'uploads/67a4a7dd57566.jpg', 1, 4, NULL, 15),
(32, 'Fortnite Leak Reveals All Chapter 6 Season 2 Update Release Dates', '<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><em><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Fortnite</span></strong></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;fans have a lot to look forward to, as the update schedule for the game has reportedly been leaked online. Despite still being several weeks away from&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Fortnite</span></em>\'s upcoming Chapter 6 Season 1 update, Epic Games has either intentionally or unintentionally revealed every date for the game\'s next content cycle, including when the next \"OG\" season launches. This news follows recent&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/db/video-game/fortnite/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Fortnite</span></em></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;events like the Godzilla x Kong collaboration, with plenty of fresh content on the way in the near future.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">It seems like no game is immune from leaks, especially&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Fortnite</span></em>, with collaborations, crossovers, and updates constantly being discovered online. While some of these leaks end up not happening, others, like&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/fortnite-iron-man-skin-rumor-2025/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Fortnite</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">\'s numerous Marvel collaborations</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;and the game\'s recent kaiju-themed update, were discovered months in advance. While leaks can ruin the surprise of an unannounced update, they can also build hype, with players eagerly awaiting&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Fortnite</span></em>\'s Chapter 6 Season 2 update, which has seemingly been fully revealed ahead of its official launch.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">According to&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://trello.com/b/GXLc34hk/epic-games-store-roadmap\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; background: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Epic Games\' public Trello board</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">, the schedule for every upcoming&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/fortnite-chapter-6-season-2-theme-leak/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; background: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Fortnite</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; background: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">&nbsp;Season 2 update</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">&nbsp;has been revealed. This board is where Epic shares incoming updates, bug fixes, and other news regarding&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Fortnite</span></em>\'s various modes. This new board indicates that Chapter 6 Season 2 will begin on February 21, 2025, as originally reported. However, another update will follow shortly on March 11, though its contents remain a mystery for now. Season 3 of&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Fortnite</span></em>&nbsp;OG launches on March 25, according to the table, continuing the game\'s incredibly popular \"back to basics\" experience that kicked off in 2024.</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">New Fortnite Leak Reveals Update Timeline</span></h2>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Chapter 6 Season 2</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;- February 21, 2025</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">v34.10</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;- March 11, 2025</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">v34.20</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;<strong>(Fortnite OG Season 3)</strong>&nbsp;- March 25, 2025</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">v34.30</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;- April 8, 2025</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">v34.40</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;- April 22, 2025</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">v35.00</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;<strong>(Chapter 6 Season 3)</strong>&nbsp;- May 2, 2025</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">Looking ahead to April, two updates are scheduled to drop, one on April 8 and one on April 22. Again, the content contained in these updates remains unknown for the time being. Assuming the table is accurate, players can expect&nbsp;<em>Fortnite</em>&nbsp;Chapter 6 Season 3 to launch on May 2. It\'s important to note these are just currently scheduled dates and are subject to change, something Epic Games itself noted on its Trello card. Epic Games is quite open about&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\"><a href=\"http://gamerant.com/fortnite-chapter-6-season-1-release-date-keyart/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Fortnite</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">&nbsp;and the game\'s various updates</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">&nbsp;and content overhauls, announcing even the smallest weapon and balance changes on its numerous social media channels.</span></p>', 'Admin', '2025-02-06 12:16:38', 'uploads/67a4a826311d7.jpg', 1, 4, NULL, 9);
