: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Then later Friday night, head to&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Stable Hall</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;for everybody&rsquo;s favorite classic country cover band&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://www.tixr.com/groups/stablehall/events/the-texases-117442\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">The Texases</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">. They rocked the joint during the grand opening concert in January, so come prepared to dance. Doors at 7 p.m.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">A Saturday song swap? Head to&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-a